{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Escape Memoirs: Questionable Side Stories is a humorous co-operative escape room game where you are looking to get hired by an international criminal organisation. Unfortunately for you, the job interview is being held in a very inconvenient location, and you must make your way through an old sewer system to get there. To make it in time, you must make good use of your wits to overcome the challenges that await you in the sewers.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Solve Puzzles</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Wide variety of simple and fun puzzles, that are sure to make you laugh, or at least to make your friends laugh at you.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2363730/extras/gif_crane.gif?t=1734637739\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2363730/extras/gif_singleRoll.gif?t=1734637739\" /></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Explore and Discover</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">You will get to enjoy exploring a dirty sewer system, as you try to make it to the job interview. There are plenty of hidden collectibles and safety violations for you to find as you make your way through the sewer.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Work Together</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Play solo, or distract your friends in up to 5-player multiplayer. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p>","achievements":{"highlighted":[{"name":"Novice Rat Collector","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2363730/b2f5d9ea6b283e9d30411fef1df7739c3e4aad27.jpg"},{"name":"Expert Rat Collector","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2363730/b4aaed828139dc9f3e461cc9b4f7d72aa2